Package: phylometrics
Title: Estimating statistical errors of phylogenetic metrics
Version: 0.1
Author: Xia Hua <xia.hua@anu.edu.au>, Lindell Bromham <lindell.bromham@anu.edu.au>
Maintainer: Xia Hua <xia.hua@anu.edu.au>
Description: phylometrics provides functions to estimate statistical errors of phylogenetic metrics particularly to detect binary trait influence on diversification, as well as a function to simulate trees with fixed number of sampled taxa and trait prevalence.
Depends: R (>= 2.1.1)
imports: mvtnorm
License: GPL (>=2)
